## GITHUB PUSH PROCESS
1. Review all changes for quality and consistency
2. Ensure no debugging code remains
3. Optimize all assets before committing
4. Write clear, descriptive commit messages
5. Push to the appropriate branch
6. Verify the deployment works correctly
7. Check for any post-deployment issues

